  "synopsis": "As a stickler for rules and a knight with the highest regard for honor, Sigrid believed her loyalty would be unswerving and true... until she is killed by the liege she serves. Just when the guillotine's blade hits her neck, she wakes up to find herself five years before her execution. With a second chance at life, Sigrid swears to change her old ways and avoid her wretched fate. Unfortunately, she soon discovers that shaking off her past may not be as easy as she had imagined... \n\n(Source: Tapas) \n\n*Note: Includes 25 extra chapters.*",
